          "type": "pillar",
          "settings": {
            "number": "02 — LEADERSHIP",
            "title": "YOUR SOVEREIGN BRAND",
            "body": "Your brand is not a mask of perception; it is the physical manifesto of your sovereign reality. If your internal competence is high but your visibility is low, you have a designed deficiency in your infrastructure. In this definitive session, Nancy Vuu equips global visionaries to stop merely \"branding\" and start architecting a sovereign visible distinction. Learn the proprietary mechanics of bridging the gap between who you are and how the world must receive you. Deconstruct the barriers between notoriety and enduring significance. It is time to don your Mantle of Authority."
